# A list of Visual Studio Code useful extensions 

* Beautify : to indent your html code 
* Bracket Pair Colorizer : to spot missing brackets 
* Indent-rainbow & Indenticator : to show indentation mistakes 
* File tree view : to see your functions architecture 
* GitLens : to help you with git
* camel_case_navigation 
* php Intelephense
* Project_manager
* French language
* file-icons : to have nice icons
* EditorConfig, to manage .editorconfig and share the same configuration with your colleagues
* PHP Debug (Xdebug) : to have a live execution of your code
